We use a third party payment provider to process payments. We do not collect personal information related to credits cards or other payment information. The payment provider will collect, use and disclose that information in accordance with its own privacy policy.
Sharing your personal information
We do not sell your personal information to third parties (as "sell" is defined in California law). A "sale" would not include a situation where someone is buying all or part of our business (as is explained further below).
We share your personal information with our employees, contractors, consultants and other parties such as affiliates and third party companies that assist us in providing our services, including marketers, customer support and hosting services. Below is a non-exhaustive list of the third parties that may have access to personal information under our control.
